[I] The ROCm™ Data Center Tool

[T] The ROCm™ Data Center Tool simplifies the administration and addresses
[T] key infrastructure challenges in AMD GPUs in cluster and datacenter
[T] environments. The main features are: - GPU telemetry - GPU statistics for
[T] jobs - Integration with third-party tools.

